Deadline Date Appeal Process | CampusCare                Search for:                 Home  About  Benefits  COVID-19 Information  Important Information   ACA & 1095B  Dates & Fees  Popular Insurance Definitions  CampusCare as secondary insurance  Quick Reference Guide  Waiver & Reinstatement Forms  Eligibility  Dependent Information  Locate Physicians  Summer Coverage  Print ID Cards  Health Service Fee  Letter of Credible Coverage  Deadline Date Appeal Process    FAQs  Policies  Claims  Physician’s Screen  Contact Us         Deadline Date Appeal Process  If you missed the deadline to waive out, add/drop dependents or continue through the Summer for CampusCare coverage AND there are any extenuating/unusual circumstances , you can submit an official Letter of Appeal explaining why the deadline was missed along with the following documentation:  Your First and Last Name Your UIN# Full Mailing Address Copy of the Front and Back of your Health Insurance Card Explanation for missing the deadline date  This information should be sent by one of the methods listed below:  By Fax: 312.413.0254  Email:  cchealth@uic.edu  By Mail: CampusCare Appeal Board 818 S. Wolcott Ave, 7th Floor, MC972 Chicago, IL 60612  Please allow 2 weeks for a decision. A letter will be mailed to the address provided on your application. Please note that appeals can be approved or denied based on the Committee’s decision .  CampusCare sends out 2 emails, to every email address the University has on file, for all registered students before the Enrollment Period Deadline Date every semester containing instructions on how to locate and submit the forms. CampusCare also speaks at all new/transfer student, parent, and college orientations regarding this information. Students who do not have extenuating/unusual circumstances will not receive an approved appeal. Being new to this school, not reading/opening your emails, or forgetting to fill out the form before the Enrollment Period Deadline Date are not extenuating or unusual circumstances and will not recieve approval of their appeal.  Students who enroll after the deadline date do not have the option of waiving coverage per CampusCare’s policy.            © Copyright 2014-2020 The Board of Trustees of the University of Illinois      Footer Navigation   University of Illinois Hospital & Health Sciences System UIC Flames CampusCare Logo Disability Resources  Emergency Information  Privacy Policy  Contact Us  COVID-19 Information          